Nomad's chronicles - part 3
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
The discovery changed the way we comprehended the world.
The monolith did not have any special powers but the ones observing it felt an inspiration of unknown strength.
New, daring ideas were shaped in our minds. New ways to see and understand things. Visions.


Some feared it.
Called its influence unnatural.
The monolith became subject of heated debates.


Supporters and opponents kept the balance until the first suicide happened.